name: Key
description:
Maples keys are caught among grapevine tendrils in winter. The details of the vascular system are back lit and made visible by the fresh bright snow. 

2017. Nikon D60, 55-200mm Lens.

Photographed in situ, without the use of artificial lighting or staging. Photoshop only used for resizing.
